// Implement a generic Stack<T> class using an ArrayList.
// Must support: push(T item), pop() -> T, peek() -> T,
// isEmpty() -> boolean, size() -> int
// Stack should throw RuntimeException if pop/peek on empty stack.
// Test with Integer and String stacks.

